00:34:59.115 --> 00:34:59.990 align:middle line:90%
>>ROSS: Yes, exactly.

00:34:59.990 --> 00:35:01.115 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: This is the time.

00:35:01.115 --> 00:35:03.730 align:middle line:84%
So that's why we have to
employ that incredible truth.

00:35:03.730 --> 00:35:06.980 align:middle line:84%
I want to get back to one
point in here before we go on.

00:35:06.980 --> 00:35:09.350 align:middle line:84%
And that is one of
the other points

00:35:09.350 --> 00:35:12.500 align:middle line:84%
that you feel free
sharing with us

00:35:12.500 --> 00:35:16.340 align:middle line:84%
is relationship existing
between the substance of mind

00:35:16.340 --> 00:35:18.380 align:middle line:90%
and the substance of spirit.

00:35:18.380 --> 00:35:20.330 align:middle line:84%
Explain that a
little bit for us.

00:35:20.330 --> 00:35:23.180 align:middle line:84%
>>ROSS: What Manly
Hall went on to say

00:35:23.180 --> 00:35:29.480 align:middle line:84%
here is the understanding
