00:35:29.480 --> 00:35:32.060 align:middle line:90%
who they are.

00:35:32.060 --> 00:35:36.890 align:middle line:84%
People just assume, all
of us, our ego, our mind

00:35:36.890 --> 00:35:37.790 align:middle line:90%
is who we are.

00:35:37.790 --> 00:35:38.360 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Our thoughts.

00:35:38.360 --> 00:35:39.235 align:middle line:90%
>>ROSS: Our thoughts.

00:35:39.235 --> 00:35:40.850 align:middle line:90%
That is who we are.

