00:36:05.313 --> 00:36:06.980 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: It's just
a sense of identity.

00:36:06.980 --> 00:36:07.220 align:middle line:90%
>>ROSS: Right.

00:36:07.220 --> 00:36:08.990 align:middle line:84%
And there's people
who have said,

00:36:08.990 --> 00:36:10.580 align:middle line:90%
I've got to get rid of my ego.

00:36:10.580 --> 00:36:12.020 align:middle line:90%
And I have to share with them--

00:36:12.020 --> 00:36:14.030 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: That's a sense of who
and what you will collectively

00:36:14.030 --> 00:36:14.540 align:middle line:90%
have become.

00:36:14.540 --> 00:36:15.340 align:middle line:90%
>>ROSS: Exactly.

00:36:15.340 --> 00:36:17.390 align:middle line:84%
What you really
are asking is, you

00:36:17.390 --> 00:36:19.910 align:middle line:90%
want to spiritualize your ego.

00:36:19.910 --> 00:36:23.870 align:middle line:84%
But if you didn't have an
ego, you wouldn't be existing.

00:36:23.870 --> 00:36:28.370 align:middle line:90%
So the substance of the spirit--

00:36:28.370 --> 00:36:32.870 align:middle line:84%
now again, the symbols
can be accepted just

00:36:32.870 --> 00:36:35.360 align:middle line:84%
by the substance
of the mind, what

00:36:35.360 --> 00:36:42.800 align:middle line:84%
the mind has been conditioned to
remember, what it has observed.

00:36:42.800 --> 00:36:44.900 align:middle line:84%
Then the mind will
look at a symbol

00:36:44.900 --> 00:36:47.930 align:middle line:84%
