00:36:49.940 --> 00:36:55.490 align:middle line:84%
But the substance of the
spirit is more encompassing.

00:36:55.490 --> 00:36:59.750 align:middle line:84%
And when we observe from
our spiritual essence

00:36:59.750 --> 00:37:04.730 align:middle line:84%
and look at things that we look
at all the time with our mind,

00:37:04.730 --> 00:37:06.620 align:middle line:90%
