create this new world the way

00:43:18.300 --> 00:43:19.260 align:middle line:90%
you want to see it.

00:43:19.260 --> 00:43:20.060 align:middle line:90%
>>ROSS: Right.

00:43:20.060 --> 00:43:24.030 align:middle line:84%
And people don't realize
"The Ancient Teachings"

00:43:24.030 --> 00:43:28.410 align:middle line:90%
