00:43:28.410 --> 00:43:33.090 align:middle line:84%
We are down here to demonstrate
how we manage creative energy.

00:43:33.090 --> 00:43:34.590 align:middle line:90%
We are creators.

00:43:34.590 --> 00:43:38.640 align:middle line:84%
We can create our world in
the way that we want to.

00:43:38.640 --> 00:43:40.920 align:middle line:84%
Someone may say, well,
but this is happening.

00:43:40.920 --> 00:43:45.150 align:middle line:84%
No, it's your
perception and how you

00:43:45.150 --> 00:43:48.570 align:middle line:84%
handle what is happening
that is going to reflect

00:43:48.570 --> 00:43:50.790 align:middle line:90%
what the outcome is for you.

00:43:50.790 --> 00:43:51.660 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Exactly.

00:43:51.660 --> 00:43:53.940 align:middle line:84%
>>ROSS: And it's always
going to be that case.

00:43:53.940 --> 00:43:54.990 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Indeed.

