00:44:23.130 --> 00:44:24.090 align:middle line:90%
To me, that's critical.

00:44:24.090 --> 00:44:24.840 align:middle line:90%
That's everything.

00:44:24.840 --> 00:44:25.640 align:middle line:90%
>>ROSS: Yes.

