right now with this thought.

00:44:33.510 --> 00:44:36.270 align:middle line:10%
Everything is possible.

00:44:36.270 --> 00:44:38.340 align:middle line:10%
We are creators.

00:44:38.340 --> 00:44:42.840 align:middle line:10%
And the more that we accent
the positive, the more positive

